  "observations": [
    "Lightning Path component renders stages as horizontal stepper with 'Mark Stage Complete' CTA and per-stage guidance panel (Key Fields + Guidance for Success)",
    "Activity timeline as universal cross-object panel — Tasks, Events, Calls, Emails, Logged Notes merged chronologically with type icons",
    "Account detail organized as tabbed shell: Details / Activity / Chatter / News / Related — each tab is a distinct projection over same record",
    "Highlights panel pinned at top of record detail with key business fields (AnnualRevenue, NumberOfEmployees, Industry, account team)",
    "Related lists below detail render child collections (Contacts, Opportunities, Cases, Quotes) with quick-create buttons",
    "Lead Conversion is a first-class composite intent producing Account + Contact + Opportunity in single form, not a generic status change",
    "Kanban view auto-derived from picklist fields (stage, status) — drag between columns advances stage",
    "Split view renders list pane left + selected detail right within same screen",
    "Inline edit on list views — pencil icon on hover, save/cancel bar appears at row level",
    "Mass actions toolbar appears when rows are selected (change owner, change status, send email, add to campaign, delete)",
    "Forecast hierarchy renders as expandable tree (rep → manager → VP) with rollup totals per category bucket (Pipeline / Best Case / Commit / Closed)",
    "Forecast manager override editable inline; submit locks the forecast period",
    "Approval flow surfaces as banner on record with Approve / Reject / Reassign actions for current approver",
    "Chatter feed embedded as tab on every record — post, @mention, comment, like, attach files",
    "Per-user saved list views with shareable scope (private / role / org)",
    "Filter logic supports AND/OR with explicit grouping syntax (e.g., '1 AND (2 OR 3)')",
    "Object permissions exposed as multi-axis matrix: Profile (base) + Permission Sets (additive stacks) + Sharing Rules (criteria-based) + Role hierarchy (manager sees report's records)",
    "Field-level security hides fields entirely from layouts/reports/API per profile",
    "Dashboard components are references to underlying Reports — refreshing dashboard re-runs all reports",
    "Report Builder uses drag-drop columns with grouping rows, summary functions (sum/avg/count), and chart on the same canvas",
    "Cross-object reports traverse relationships (Account → Opportunities → Products) declaratively",
    "Flow Builder renders as visual canvas with elements (decision, loop, action, screen, get/create/update/delete records, subflow)",
    "Einstein scoring badges render inline on Lead/Opportunity rows (Hot/Warm/Cold; predicted-to-close %)",
    "Auto-sync from Gmail/Outlook surfaces Activities without manual logging — captured emails/events appear in timeline",
    "Person Account is a dual-mode entity (B2C) — Account and Contact merged into single record while preserving both APIs",
    "Custom objects (__c suffix) and custom fields are first-class — admin UI generates layouts, list views, and tabs automatically",
    "Utility bar at bottom of app shell hosts global tools (Phone dialer, Recent Items, Notes) persistent across navigation",
    "Lookup vs master-detail vs junction relationships have distinct cascade semantics — master-detail propagates delete and ownership",
    "Stage history is auto-tracked audit trail (from/to stage, who, when, amount/probability snapshot)",
    "Mobile cards re-layout same record with abbreviated highlights + voice-search + offline edit queue",
    "Today screen on mobile aggregates meetings + tasks + suggested follow-ups as composite dashboard",
    "Quote lock is irreversible business state — locked quote cannot be edited, only cloned",
    "Order activation transitions Draft → Activated and is irreversible",
    "Mark Lost requires reason form (loss reason picklist) — irreversible deal closure",
    "App Launcher grid switches subset of objects + tabs + utility bar (Sales / Service / Marketing apps)"
  ]
}